---
import RealestateLayout from '../../../layouts/RealestateLayout.astro';
import CtaButton from '../../../components/CtaButton.astro';
import NewsletterSignup from '../../../components/NewsletterSignup.astro';
---

<RealestateLayout
  title="Richmond Hill Real Estate | Neighbourhood Profile | Cory Wong, Real Estate Agent"
  description="Richmond Hill real estate neighbourhood profile: housing types, price ranges, schools, transit, and market insights from Cory Wong, Real Estate Agent, Trustwell Realty Inc., Brokerage."
  canonicalPath="/neighbourhoods/richmond-hill"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Richmond Hill Real Estate: A Neighbourhood Profile</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__subtitle">
        Cory Wong, Real Estate Agent | Trustwell Realty Inc., Brokerage
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="profile">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="profile__content">
        <p class="profile__intro">
          Richmond Hill sits between Toronto and Newmarket and draws buyers who want a mid-size
          city with strong schools, good parks, and GTA access. It's a family market, with
          demand driven largely by buyers choosing space and school quality over proximity to
          downtown.
        </p>

        <h2>Character and Feel</h2>
        <p>
          Richmond Hill has a mix of established post-war neighbourhoods and newer developments
          in the north. The Oak Ridges Moraine forms the northern boundary, giving the city a
          natural edge and limiting further northward growth. That constraint has supported
          long-term property values.
        </p>
        <p>
          The city has a diverse population, with significant Iranian, Chinese, and South Asian
          communities. Yonge Street runs through the city centre, connecting it north to Aurora
          and south toward Toronto.
        </p>

        <h2>Who Buys in Richmond Hill</h2>
        <p>
          Move-up buyers from Toronto and North York are the core buyer group. First-time buyers
          who want a detached home and find Toronto prices out of reach are also active here.
          Investors buy for long-term appreciation and rental income from York University,
          Seneca, and professionals commuting into the city.
        </p>

        <h2>Housing Types and Price Ranges</h2>
        <ul class="price-list">
          <li><strong>Detached homes:</strong> approximately $1.2M to $2.8M (north end commands a premium for newer builds and larger lots)</li>
          <li><strong>Semi-detached and freehold townhomes:</strong> $850K to $1.3M</li>
          <li><strong>Condos along Yonge Street and near the GO station:</strong> from approximately $550K</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="profile__disclaimer">
          Price ranges are general estimates based on early 2026 activity. Cory will give you a
          current assessment for your specific criteria.
        </p>

        <h2>Transit and Highways</h2>
        <p>
          Richmond Hill is accessible via Highway 404/DVP and Highway 400. The Barrie GO line
          serves the Richmond Hill GO station, with train service to Union Station. York Region
          Transit connects the city to TTC subway at Finch and Sheppard.
        </p>
        <p>
          The Yonge Street rapid bus corridor provides frequent service south into North York.
        </p>

        <h2>Amenities and Schools</h2>
        <p>
          Richmond Green Sports Centre and park, Elgin West Community Centre, and a network of
          trails along the Oak Ridges Moraine serve families well. Retail is concentrated along
          Yonge Street and the Highway 7 corridors.
        </p>
        <p>
          Richmond Hill High School and Alexander Mackenzie High School are the main public
          secondary schools. The York Catholic District School Board has several well-regarded
          schools in the area.
        </p>

        <h2>Real Estate Perspective</h2>
        <p>
          Richmond Hill has been a stable market. Prices have been resilient compared to inner
          Toronto. Inventory grew in 2025 and into 2026, giving buyers more options than at the
          2021-2022 peak. Sellers in Richmond Hill need to price to current conditions.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you're buying in Richmond Hill, the north end near Bond Lake is different from the
          mid-city Yonge Street corridor. Understanding which sub-area fits your priorities
          matters before committing to a search.
        </p>

        <div class="profile__cta">
          <CtaButton href="/contact" label="Book a Consultation" variant="primary" />
        </div>

        <p class="profile__compliance">
          Cory Wong, Real Estate Agent. Real estate services provided through Trustwell Realty
          Inc., Brokerage.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <NewsletterSignup heading="Get GTA Market Updates" />
</RealestateLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .profile {
    padding: 0 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .profile__content {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .profile__intro {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .profile__content h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .profile__content p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .price-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .price-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .price-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .profile__disclaimer {
    font-size: 0.8125rem !important;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .profile__cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .profile__compliance {
    font-size: 0.8125rem !important;
    opacity: 0.7;
    font-style: italic;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }
</style>
